summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition of rights-of-way and right-of-way easements for Laurelhurst Trunk Sewer; Seward Park Trunk Sewer; East Marginal Way extension of the Henderson Street Trunk Sewer, and providing for the acquisition in fee simple by condemnation of the Sewage Pumping Plant Site on East Marginal Way for the Henderson Street Trunk Sewer, and appropriation money therefor.
